parameters: This is the story of a girl named Rui.

She wandered into a different world called Roots.
There, she obtained magical powers known as Sol.

The world of Roots, on the brink of collapse. A
world overrun by monsters, Roots.

A tragic outcome that would have occurred had one
thing gone wrong.

Rui repelled them and, as Sol Rui, prevented the
collapse of the other world.
And so, Rui safely returned to her original world.

However, she could not return to exactly the same
life as before.

Having once connected to another world,
occasionally monsters would appear in this world
and cause incidents.

Driven by her strong sense of justice, she would
travel alone under the guise of a trip and save
people from monsters with the power of Sol.

As always tonight, she secretly vanquished
monsters and protected someone's peace before it
ended.
Tonight, her fate will be greatly decided.
This is the last one, I suppose.
Sorry, but I won't hold back.
I can see you, come out!
Yes, well, of course. I can speak.

Nunu!!? I would be troubled to be lumped together
with those unintelligent monsters from earlier!
I am a demon. De. Mon!

Demons... I've met them several times when I was
sent to the other world, but this is the first
time meeting one in the original world.
My apologies... So, what is this demon doing here?

You are surprisingly strong. To think you're just
a girl at first glance.

Sol! I know about it! Sol is the ancient magician!
I never imagined they would be in this world!!

They say don't judge a book by its cover. Indeed,
no wonder you're so strong.
So, what are you doing here?

Lately, several women have gone missing in this
town.

There's no physical evidence, and it's being
called a case of spirited away.

You see, as Sol, I can sense it. The remnants of
magical power left at the scene of the incident.

It's the same magical aura that's leaking out from
you right now!

No, you've got it all wrong! I also wandered into
this world and didn't understand anything!

I can't just starve to death! When humans wander
around defenselessly... well, it's hard to resist,
you know?

They look so tasty, I thought maybe it'd be okay
to have just a little taste...

Are you talking about the missing humans or me
getting lost?

\n<Tuberose>Saying 'please to meet you' makes it harder to
kill me, right~?
\n<Rui>...Can you return all the women you've taken?

\n<Tuberose>Ah~ that's impossible. Some of them are already
beyond help.

\n<Rui>...What about releasing the women who are still
alive?

\n<Tuberose>That's also impossible. It's not possible for them
to come back here.

\n<Rui>After doing such heinous acts... you want to save
yourself?

\n<Rui>Well, your greeting strategy worked. I'll probably
feel terrible after killing you.
\n<Rui>So... I'll make it quick and painless for you.
\n<Tuberose>Oh! Wait! Can I at least talk about my abilities?

\n<Tuberose>Well, it's just... I don't like the idea of being
killed off as just another monster...

\n<Tuberose>Ah- to be remembered as a strong opponent... seems
less regrettable, I guess.

\n<Rui>If you make even the slightest suspicious move,
I'll cut you down... if that's okay, then I'll
listen to your last words.

\n<Tuberose>Well~ my ability is called 'Eternal
Dream Training Hell Game'.

\n<Tuberose>This ability can only be used on human women, and
ones that I can be sexually excited by.

\n<Tuberose>Moreover, if my technique is broken, I lose my
life as the price!
\n<Tuberose>Well, it's not a rule that I decided.

\n<Tuberose>Once the technique is activated, it drags the
woman into a different dimension. I call this
space "Infernal Prison."

\n<Tuberose>There, the woman will challenge the doors that
appear in the different dimension as a player.

\n<Tuberose>Yes, this technique is literally a game. Killing
between the player and master is strictly
forbidden. If you attempt to kill, a penalty will
occur.

\n<Tuberose>Each room has its own rules, and various
hindrances are prepared to sexually and mentally
subjugate the player.

\n<Tuberose>If all the doors are conquered, the player is
released and I die.

\n<Tuberose>If the player's spirit breaks from not being able
to withstand the game, they lose. Their mind and
body will become my possessions.

\n<Tuberose>In other words, it's a game where lives are at
stake.
\n<Tuberose>Are you so scared that you've lost your words?

\n<Rui>No, I'm just taken aback... What's with that
roundabout and insidious nature...?

\n<Rui>And why does someone with an appearance like yours
limit it to human girls?

\n<Tuberose>Actually, despite how I look, I was originally
human...

\n<Tuberose>When I sold my soul to a demon, I wished to
completely subjugate women...
\n<Tuberose>And this is what happened to me.

\n<Rui>That's what you get for wishing for such terrible
things... You didn't want to end up looking like
that, did you?

\n<Tuberose>Or should I say... I've almost forgotten about my
human self...

\n<Rui>Hey, have you actually used that long-named
technique before?
\n<Tuberose>Yes, I've used it quite a bit.

\n<Rui>Assuming your story isn't a lie, and you're still
alive and well...
\n<Tuberose>It's been the best life, if I do say so myself.

\n<Rui>...I'm glad I listened. It's made it easier to
feel less guilty about erasing you.
\n<Tuberose>Uh, um, about this ability... it's not over yet!

\n<Rui>You've already made quite an impression on my
memory, albeit a terrible one.

\n<Tuberose>The technique 'Phantasmal Eternal Obedience Hell
Play' has certain activation conditions...

\n<Tuberose>No magic power or spells are needed, just honestly
disclose all details of this ability without
hiding anything...

\n<Tuberose>Game Master, Tuberose! Player, Rui! The eternal
dream of training in the prison of lust has been
established!!!

\n<Rui>I've been deceived... Just as terrible as you
look.

\n<Tuberose>Fufufu! In fact, I am not a pitiful eyeball that
wandered into this world by chance!

\n<Tuberose>Miss Rui! My target has been you from the
beginning!!

\n<Tuberose>I have crossed over to this world and have been
diligently gathering information! All to capture
you!

\n<Rui>Do you know? That kind of behavior is called
stalking in this world.

\n<Tuberose>Yes, I know! It's a basic rule to learn about the
environment of your enemy to know their
weaknesses.

\n<Tuberose>However, Miss Rui. You do not understand the
immense power of the Sol that has been entrusted
to you!!

\n<Tuberose>The magical power of Sol! It is the source of
power that can sustain the world!

\n<Tuberose>A young girl who does not realize her own value,
without any guards, hiding her power, and acting
alone!

\n<Tuberose>Miss Rui, do you know? In this country, such a
person is called an easy mark.

\n<Tuberose>Now manifest! The endless corridor! The ranks of
doors that pierce the horizon!

\n<Tuberose>Corrode the heart! Instill carnal desires!! Devour
the woman completely!!!
